data.description: Welcome to your dream home where every detail is designed for comfort and entertainment! This home is situated in a prime location only 5 minutes away from Georgetown’s famous historic town square. Entertain at home or head to town square for some retail therapy and delicious food. The backyard is your personal oasis, featuring a beautiful pool for both relaxation and entertainment. For larger gatherings head to the neighborhood pool and park located across the street for your celebration. This home isn’t short of entertainment opportunities indoors either! The flex space upstairs is perfect for the movie theater room of your dreams and is already prewired for surround sound. The downstairs office/flexroom, with a door leading to the outside patio, offers a dedicated space for work or relaxation.  Need extra storage? The shed, complete with power, has you covered. This home is not only convenient but also efficient, your home is equipped with two upgraded AC units, a one-year-old water heater, and an upgraded dishwasher, ensuring comfort and efficiency. The upgraded sliding glass door and solar screens contribute to energy efficiency, while recent interior repainting adds a fresh touch. Additional features include a water softener system, a microwave less than a year old, and upgraded pool equipment—pump, filter, and valves.
